ChompOn,is,a,group,buying,platform,for,publishers,It,provides,functionality,for,websites,to,integrate,group,buying,options,and,deals,across,a,network,of,publishers,ChompOn,also,analyzes,users,social,media,for,optimization,Their,RESTful,API,exposes,the,platform,s,structure,for,developers,to,expand,publishers,services,on,top,of,it,as,well,as,for,integration,with,other,services,It,can,provide,responses,in,JSON,or,XML